<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-52-1036 </DOCNO><TEXT>The contribution intends to give a survey on the most important fire protectionmeasures within the total installations of buildings, also valid fornon-residence houses and buildings of special type and use (this beinga continuation of the paper 'Fire protection in building services').Not only informations are to be conveyed, but also the insight into the- often disagreeable - fire protection injunctions, as well as the necessityof careful planning and installation work.</TEXT></DOC>